GET Directory List Example
server  -->  python3 ltwo/server.py -v
client  -->  python3 lone/main.py get 127.0.0.1

GET File Examples
server  -->  python3 ltwo/server.py -v
client  -->  python3 lone/main.py get 127.0.0.1/REAMDE.md

server  -->  python3 ltwo/server.py -v -d ./ltwo/lib
client  -->  python3 lone/main.py get 127.0.0.1/detailedusage.py

POST Example
server  -->  python3 ltwo/server.py -v -d ./ltwo
client  -->  python3 lone/main.py post -h Content-Type:application/json --f ltwo/body1.txt 127.0.0.1/test_file.txt